The review confirms the gap: `fetch_pull_request_snapshot_with_command` produces actionable error strings, but `HostGithubEnvironment` drops them by converting `Result` to `Option`, so operator output can’t distinguish “missing PR” from “`gh` unavailable/auth broken.” I’m fixing that slice now with tests first, even though I can’t execute them in this sandbox.
